|-----------|-------|------------------|
| create_issue_single | Empty DB | Single issue insert latency |
| create_issue_batch_100 | Empty DB | 100 issue batch insert |
| list_issues_100 | 100 issues | Query 100 issues latency |
| list_issues_1000 | 1000 issues | Query 1000 issues latency |
| list_issues_filtered | 1000 issues | Filtered query latency |
| update_issue_single | 100 issues | Single field update |
| close_issue_with_reason | 100 issues | Close + reason write |

### Sync Operations (benches/sync_bench.rs)
