- [ ] benches/benchmarks.rs with 18+ benchmarks
- [ ] Scaling benchmarks for 100/500/1000/5000 issues
- [ ] HTML reports generated
- [ ] Logging captures timing at each stage
- [ ] CI workflow stores baseline metrics
- [ ] Regression detection threshold: 10%

